9b8861d4bcb55ca9e5a834f1185d188a4c7f970e.query:
SELECT kavasam_hashes.hash
                FROM kavasam_hashes
                INNER JOIN
                    kavasam_reports
                ON
                    kavasam_hashes.ID = kavasam_reports.hash_id
                INNER JOIN 
                    kavasam_users
                ON
                    kavasam_users.ID = kavasam_reports.reported_by
                WHERE
                    kavasam_users.public_key = $1
                AND
                    kavasam_hashes.id_type = $2

a67da1601f58d7daaefe345d62f3958bdfab4d2c.query:
SELECT kavasam_hashes.hash, kavasam_hashes.id_type
                FROM kavasam_hashes
                INNER JOIN
                    kavasam_reports
                ON
                    kavasam_hashes.ID = kavasam_reports.hash_id
                INNER JOIN 
                    kavasam_users
                ON
                    kavasam_users.ID = kavasam_reports.reported_by
                WHERE
                    kavasam_users.public_key = $1
